			<description><![CDATA[<p>
<strong>GlobalTranz is a freight management company specializing in Less-Than-Truckload, Full Truckload, Supply Chain Management, and Domestic Air/Expedited shipping. We focus on innovative technology and partnering with sales professionals that possess energy, insight and a fervent customer service mentality. As one of the fastest growing transportation companies in the country, we have been recognized by the Inc.500 and received the Phoenix Business Journal&rsquo;s Arizona Corporate Excellence award, as the 2nd and 5th fastest growing companies in the state, for 2011 and 2012. With annual sales of over $150M, GlobalTranz has been able to double every year since our inception in 2003.</strong></p>
<p>
GlobalTranz has secured competitive pricing with thousands of national, regional, and local carriers. We leverage the infrastructure, systems, and personnel of world-class carriers to your benefit. Through our proprietary TMS solution, CarrierRate.com, customers are able to rate, schedule, and manage their LTL shipments with a few clicks. For your larger accounts, our team of highly skilled rate negotiators will procure Customer Specific Pricing with multiple carriers.</p>
<p>
<strong>Description of the Opportunity:</strong><br />
With this opportunity, you will own your own Transportation and Logistics business while partnering with GlobalTranz. In addition, we handle all of the back-end office work including: invoicing, receivables, credit, collections, claims, obtaining Customer Specific Pricing, and of course top-notch support. You receive a minimum of 50% of the profit for LTL shipments with unlimited earnings potential. You are paid every 15 days, based on booked shipments. In essence, we pay you before we collect from the customer.</p>
<p>
This entrepreneurial model works because our Agents use a consultative approach and leverage our competitive pricing and highly technological way of managing freight. Your focus as an Agent is to obtain and maintain customers while building equity in your own company. This program has been proven by over 200 freight sales professionals nationwide.</p>
<p>
Where else can you start your own freight sales business with virtually no startup costs and immediately offer a best-in-class TMS, as well as pricing from an extensive list of carriers?</p>
<p>
<strong>The GlobalTranz Agent Program offers:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
The ability to sell a full portfolio of services including LTL, FTL, Air/Expedited and Supply Chain services. You are a one stop shop for your customers&rsquo; freight needs!</li>
<li>
Proprietary TMS, CarrierRate.com, the most advanced, user friendly, technology in the freight industry</li>
<li>
Extremely competitive rates with many LTL carriers, thousands of FTL carriers, and major air carriers</li>
<li>
Complete sales and operational training at our corporate office in Phoenix, AZ</li>
<li>
Full support to help you manage your customers</li>
<li>
Robust back-end CRM tool with KPIs, visibility tools and accounting functions</li>
<li>
Monthly Sales Conference calls</li>
<li>
Full Supply Chain Department to manage warehousing and inventory opportunities</li>
<li>
Full Pricing Department to help you secure larger accounts</li>
<li>
We advance you your portion of the profits</li>
<li>
Unlimited earnings</li>
<li>
The ability to sell your book of business at a later date</li>
<li>
Annual Agent Convention and Award Ceremony</li>
<li>
Referral Bonuses paid when you bring on new successful Agents</li>
</ul>
<p>
&nbsp;</p>
<p>
<strong>Minimum Requirements:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Minimum 2 years of freight sales experience (broker school does not qualify as experience)</li>
<li>
Possess a current book of business/relationships with multiple shippers</li>
</ul>
